       describe("Quote - policy-wide modifiers", () => {
         // 1 passing (loyalty -20%), 2 todo (first insurance, follow-up discount)
       });
       describe("Quote - integration", () => {
         // 2 todo (newcomer 165G, long-standing 160G)
       });
       describe("Quote - rounding", () => { /* 1 todo */ });
       describe("Claim - reimbursement", () => { /* 4 todo */ });
       describe("Claim - cap and successive claims", () => { /* 3 todo */ });
       describe("Claim - rounding", () => { /* 1 todo */ });
       describe("Error handling", () => { /* 4 todo */ });
     });
     ```

   - **`src/claim-office.ts`** - Implementation file. Current full state:
     ```typescript
